escena 1: presentacion de nombres y explicacion de que es un cultivo hidroponico


YOAN:"Have you ever wondered if plants can grow without a single handful of soil? Welcome to the world of hydroponics."

JHON:"In a hydroponic system, soil is replaced by a mineral-rich water solution. This allows plants to get their nutrients directly through their roots, with zero effort."

JHON:"The results? It uses up to 90% less water than traditional farming, takes up less space, and helps crops grow significantly faster."

YOAN:"From vertical farms to your own kitchen, hydroponics is the future of sustainable, fresh food. Efficient, clean, and incredibly smart."

